1. create directory with multiple "roles"
2. each role is called as a object mapped to an openAI api call
3. any response from the openAI api call is fed back as a conversation item
4. conversation items are used as input to openAI with target role assumed
5. continue playing hot potatoe with replies from openAI until task is achieved.
6. each role is assigned duties which when combined and fulfilled, achieve the desired outcome.
7. add a pixelart UI
8. (if Xinese) - call china database (scraping openAI)
